Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺德拉姆入港准备 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队旗舰阿马迪厄斯来电
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令官 您终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报敌舰接近…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马迪厄斯完成补给后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即刻出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这艘船上执行舰队指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以参谋长身份登舰后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号即是舰队旗舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…那艘船？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们旨在占领地球圈的重要生产卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺德拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其与移动要塞达乌内斯强行对接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为攻略地球的前线基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用诺德拉姆内的工业生产能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我军补给机能大幅提高
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 卫星居民既可作为劳动力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人将无法轻易向我们发动进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！这种作战的成功可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是伊泽尔坎特大人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回我们的故乡地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的时刻到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.57,0:01:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你 菲利特
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重申一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作战 以天神号为旗舰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽坐镇舰桥指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还须天神号舰长协助司令部运转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾丝中校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近处看上去还真俊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 各舰来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰队 开始出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神号 慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前线更易作出精确指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这场战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要返回火星圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内人不曾冰眠 时光蹉跎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共度最后的时光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难为你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们告诉我作战部署
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是预备队？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不安排我去最前线？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 德西尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保后备兵源是战术之本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为防万一 命令你待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对菲利特·明日野 你有特殊的感情在作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样上战场…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么错！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要嘣了菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 我活到今天的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再放任他了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何做？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会考虑处分的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现敌人舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 是击退那些人类公敌的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 开始布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环形阵列 准备启动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为电磁终端输入坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军最新武器 光子环形阵列是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是将电磁终端呈圆环状排列在宇宙空间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令电子在内侧旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造出强大的动能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用天神号的光子爆破炮完成指向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如何不被敌人察觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环充电完成前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得让敌人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我们要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为此需要做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗到最后的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论对手是谁 都要战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗虽苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是失去战友会更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住了吗 要活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 一定活着要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 奥布莱特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不合时宜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次…关于求婚的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如…如果不嫌弃我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发咯 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达 一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达AGE-2 巴雷特双枪 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Bouncer 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队 奥布莱特·洛伦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Genoace-2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克斯·哈特维 Adele-1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎·甘海尔 Adele-2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的作战太蛮干了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您必须三思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多勒 想想我们家乡的惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便以生命为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要实现伊泽尔坎特大人理想中的伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的未来 只存在于伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这双手打开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往未来的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁终端 部署完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 电子加速开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子加速程序开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 天神号没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 巴雷特双枪的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次那个X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 这高达不是菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不腻味也难
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二战队 追击敌机动战士队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游击部队投入作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪阵是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫使我方集中兵力 引诱我们中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩挲副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让达乌内斯紧急调头 朝向坐标F21方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 机动战士队正准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令他们停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推进系统应急模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军已经完成了那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…这么快？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急通知全军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止追击敌人 立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 好不容易突破阵线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环形阵列
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射环确认形成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入最终程序
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 准备指向射击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军 撤离光子阵列射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人战线后方 侦测到强力光子辐射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癸干忒斯之盾 系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指向射击 准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子爆破炮 指向发射
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未发现重大损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子光束遭到扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌要塞没有受损
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人似乎部署了某种干涉掩体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然当场化解了我们的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾的联邦 藏着那种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以司令官下令暂时撤退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体…不听使唤…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙我对付得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿莉莎她们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 快去救队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和没事…有点差距
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长 我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从外面帮你打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 亚瑟姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 你是个尽让人操心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我如果做得更好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出 你是个厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是X-Rounder 也够厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个超级机师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个天下无敌的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我厉害得多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙第一的机师…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…看好你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫少校的G-Bouncer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号…消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆 沃尔夫呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有人从我的面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 迄今为止多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提多尽兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当救世主的豪言壮语 要兑现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蕾丝舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环阵列的状态如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光子环阵列再充填 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你 绝不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲法和涅特的识别信号消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生 他们死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为他们报仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐标 F28宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 不许靠近那片宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲法和涅特是被德西尔操纵才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的话你们也会步他们的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那里还有高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在的实力无法估量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子不是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预…预判不出 为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是X-Rounder！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级机师…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.08,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆·明日野！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有输的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有输的道理！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对亲哥哥也见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一开始就是这么打算的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意言辞 多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要成为障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓会不择手段抵达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现伊泽尔坎特大人梦想的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人为什么丝毫没有攻击诺德拉姆的迹象？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.32,0:21:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令全军向敌移动要塞发起总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括诺德拉姆守军在内
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部兵力投入作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目的不是毁灭卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯 这里拜托了
